{"id":599,"date":"2022-02-16T12:17:29","date_gmt":"2022-02-16T12:17:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/?page_id=599"},"modified":"2022-02-16T12:17:30","modified_gmt":"2022-02-16T12:17:30","slug":"blocks","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/blocks\/","title":{"rendered":"Blocks"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>KnowAll includes an exclusive selection of blocks for building your knowledge base content.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lists<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-list heroic-styled-list\" id=\"heroic-styled-list-3de84ba1-45be-46bc-a73f-4d837310f8bf\"><ol class=\"fa-ul\"><li>Lists are a great way of walking users through a process <strong>step by step<\/strong>.<\/li><li>You can direct users via images:<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"734\" height=\"400\" class=\"wp-image-295\" style=\"width: 450px;\" src=\"https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2016\/03\/knowall-responsive.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2016\/03\/knowall-responsive.png 734w, https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2016\/03\/knowall-responsive-300x163.png 300w, https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2016\/03\/knowall-responsive-50x27.png 50w, https:\/\/demo.herothemes.com\/knowall\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/23\/2016\/03\/knowall-responsive-60x33.png 60w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 734px) 100vw, 734px\" \/><\/li><li>Finally this is step 3.<\/li><\/ol><style>#heroic-styled-list-3de84ba1-45be-46bc-a73f-4d837310f8bf li:before{\n\t\t                   background:#00b4b3;\n\t\t                   border-radius: 0;\n\t\t                   }<\/style><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Messages<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-messages wp-block-hb-message wp-block-hb-message--withicon is-style-info\"><strong>Tip<\/strong>: This is a callout. You can use these to highlight important information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-messages wp-block-hb-message wp-block-hb-message--withicon\"><strong>Success:<\/strong> Let visitors see how to do things right<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-messages wp-block-hb-message wp-block-hb-message--withicon is-style-alert\"><strong>Advice:<\/strong> Flag warnings in-content.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-messages wp-block-hb-message wp-block-hb-message--withicon is-style-danger\"><strong>Danger:<\/strong> Highlight danger warnings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Toggles<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-toggle wp-block-hb-toggle\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-toggle__title\"><span>Extras<\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-toggle__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-toggle__contentwrap\">Reveal further information here.<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tabs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-tabs wp-block-hb-tabs\"><ul class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__nav\" role=\"tablist\"><li class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head\" data-tab=\"tabs-0\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"active\"><span class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head_item\" for=\"tab0\">Windows<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head\" data-tab=\"tabs-1\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"inactive\"><span class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head_item\" for=\"tab1\">Mac OS<\/span><\/li><li class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head\" data-tab=\"tabs-2\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"inactive\"><span class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__head_item\" for=\"tab2\">Android<\/span><\/li><\/ul><div id=\"tabs-0\" class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__content\" role=\"tabpanel\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"active\"><p>See different information based on the selected tab.<\/p><\/div><div id=\"tabs-1\" class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__content\" role=\"tabpanel\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"inactive\"><p>For example, different versions or operating systems.<\/p><\/div><div id=\"tabs-2\" class=\"wp-block-hb-tabs__content\" role=\"tabpanel\" data-hb-tabs-tab--state=\"inactive\"><p>It can all be done right from the editor with the blocks included in KnowAll.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Accordion<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-ht-blocks-accordion wp-block-hb-accordion\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__section\" data-ht-blocks-accordion-block-state=\"closed\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__title\"><span>Step One<\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__contentwrap\">Break content into sections, to ease readability.<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__section\" data-ht-blocks-accordion-block-state=\"closed\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__title\"><span>Step Two<\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__contentwrap\">You can create sections using the WordPress editor.<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__section\" data-ht-blocks-accordion-block-state=\"closed\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__title\"><span>Step Three<\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-hb-accordion__contentwrap\">Use for stepped progress and more.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>All these blocks are included with the KnowAll knowledge base theme package.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>KnowAll includes an exclusive selection of blocks for building your knowledge base content. Lists Messages Toggles Tabs Accordion All these blocks are included with the KnowAll knowledge base theme package.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\